{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, with a large amount of data training, the deep learning approach can learn the intrinsic laws of the data and has a better prediction ability for new data that have not been previously described.",
    "These attributes ensure high accuracy and reliability when various problems are addressed.",
    "However, such methods require a large amount of data for training; otherwise, they are prone to overfitting.",
    "In knowledge Q&A, this requirement means that many Q&A pairs and related knowledge need to be collected and processed to ensure accuracy and generalizability.",
    "In practical applications, obtaining high-quality Q&A data and related knowledge is often a considerable challenge."
  ]
}